Logos and Graphics
******************

.[perex]
Do you need the official framework logo? Would you like to put the framework icon on your website? Then you've come to the right place.


Please always write the framework name in the form **Nette Framework**, without (R) or (TM). It would be great if you could phrase your sentences so that the name does not need to be inflected.

Because the framework name is protected by a "trademark":[http://isdv.upv.cz/portal/pls/portal/portlets.ozs.det?pozk=2785136&plan=en], its use comes with certain restrictions. We appreciate that you support Nette Framework by creating new web services related to it, but we must ask you not to use "Nette" in the names of your products or in top-level domains. Instead, try to choose an abbreviation (e.g. "N" or "NF") or some other variant.


Logo
----

The Nette Framework logo is a fundamental building block of a unified visual style. It consists of a distinctive typographic rendering of the word "nette" and may be accompanied by the word "framework".

.[logo]
- [* nette-logo-black.webp *] .[img]
- "Vector format for printing":attachment:NetteFramework-vector-logo.zip
- "600x300 for web":attachment:nette-logo-black.png

.[logo]
