Colors
------

The Nette Framework logo reproduction will look best if you keep the official color palette, representing the blue sunny sky and the creamy foam of a good espresso.

.[logocolors]
- <div style="background:#3484D2"></div>
 **Blue**
 Pantone 2925 C
 RGB 52, 132, 210
 HEX #3484D2

.[logocolors]
- <div style="background:#9E8541"></div>
 **Cream**
 Pantone 4505 C
 RGB 158, 133, 65
 HEX #9E8541


